re</i>. It was a very popular name in medieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Walter Wardlaw was born in 1240, in Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland as the son of Henricus de Wardlaw. He had at least 1 son. He died in Scotland, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1240–":"1240–Surnud","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","1268–1358":"1268–1358","1220–Male":"1220–Surnud","1358":"1358","1268":"1268","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland":"Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1240–":"1240–Kuollut","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","1268–1358":"1268–1358","1220–Male":"1220–Kuollut","1358":"1358","1268":"1268","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland":"Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1240–":"1240–Décédé","1240–Male":"1240–Décédé","1268–1358":"1268–1358","1220–Male":"1220–Décédé","1358":"1358","1268":"1268","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland":"Wilton, Roxburghshire, Écosse","Scotland":"Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Walter Wardlaw est né en 1240, à Wilton, Roxburghshire, Écosse, fils de Henricus de Wardlaw. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé à Écosse, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1240–":"1240–Verstorben","1240–Male":"1240–Verstorben","1268–1358":"1268–1358","1220–Male":"1220–Verstorben","1358":"1358","1268":"1268","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland":"Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Walter Wardlaw wurde 1240 in Wilton, Roxburghshire, Scotland, als Sohn von Henricus de Wardlaw geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb in Schottland, United Kingdom."},"ht":{"1240–":"1240–Desede","1240–Male":"1240–Desede","1268–1358":"1268–1358","1220–Mal